title: gesserit's favourites: First Issues for May 2015
description:
Cover:     <a href=" http://gesserit.000space.com/meta/yuq/users/29/766/LuoHeiFBDG.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://gesserit.000space.com/meta/yuq/users/29/766/LuoHeiFBDG.png</a>





Contains:   Arcadia       001 (2015) (Digital)            (Vee-Empire)

            Harrow County 001 (2015) (Digital)             (Minutemen-InnerDemons)

            Mythic        001 (2015) (Digital)  (Son of Ultron-Empire)

            Pisces        001 (2015) (Digital)           (Zone-Empire)

            The Mantle    001 (2015) (Digital)           (Zone-Empire)



            After the "spring high" of the previous two months, we're down to a more
            usual total of five series this time, with Image contributing the by-now
            expected three, and Boom Studios and Dark Horse one each. The weirdness
            factor of these books is likely at an all-time high, though, even after
            accounting for comics usually being somewhat stranger than is typical
            in other (more constrained) media - don't say I didn't warn ya! ;)
